sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor Source as External Source<br/>(User or API)
    participant FE as Frontend<br/>(React SPA)
    participant BE as Backend Services<br/>(NestJS :3002)
    participant Auth as Auth Module<br/>(JWT / API Key)
    participant Blob as Blob Storage<br/>(local / Azure)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>(Prisma)
    participant TS as Temporal Server<br/>(:7233)
    participant TW as Temporal Worker<br/>(graphWorkflow)
    participant ADI as Azure Document<br/>Intelligence
    participant HITL as HITL Queue

    Note over Source,HITL: DOCUMENT UPLOAD & WORKFLOW TRIGGER

    Source ->> FE: Upload document (browser)
    Note right of Source: Or: API consumer POSTs<br/>directly to Backend<br/>with x-api-key header
    FE ->> BE: POST /api/upload<br/>(file + metadata + JWT)
    BE ->> Auth: Validate JWT or API key
    Auth -->> BE: Authenticated (user ID)
    BE ->> Blob: Save file → blobKey<br/>(documents/{id}/original.pdf)
    BE ->> DB: INSERT Document<br/>(status: pre_ocr,<br/>workflow_config_id, model_id)
    BE ->> DB: SELECT Workflow config<br/>(GraphWorkflowConfig JSON)
    BE ->> BE: Compute configHash<br/>(SHA-256 canonical)
    BE ->> TS: Start graphWorkflow<br/>(graph, initialCtx:{documentId,<br/>blobKey, fileName, modelId},<br/>configHash)
    TS -->> BE: workflowExecutionId
    BE ->> DB: UPDATE Document<br/>(workflow_execution_id)
    BE -->> FE: 201 Created (documentId)

    Note over TS,ADI: STANDARD OCR PATH (Temporal Worker)

    TS ->> TW: Dispatch task
    TW ->> DB: document.updateStatus<br/>→ ongoing_ocr

    rect rgb(239, 246, 255)
        Note over TW,ADI: OCR Pipeline
        TW ->> Blob: file.prepare<br/>(resolve blob path, validate)
        TW ->> ADI: azureOcr.submit<br/>(POST document for analysis)
        ADI -->> TW: operationId / apimRequestId
        TW ->> DB: document.updateStatus<br/>(store apimRequestId)

        loop pollUntil node (interval: 10s, max: 20)
            TW ->> ADI: azureOcr.poll<br/>(GET operation status)
            ADI -->> TW: status: running / succeeded
        end

        TW ->> TW: azureOcr.extract<br/>(parse Azure response)
        TW ->> TW: ocr.cleanup<br/>(normalize text)
        TW ->> TW: ocr.checkConfidence<br/>(compute average, flag if below threshold)
    end

    Note over TW,HITL: CONDITIONAL ROUTING (switch node)

    alt Confidence >= threshold
        TW ->> DB: ocr.storeResults<br/>(upsert OcrResult with keyValuePairs)
        TW ->> DB: document.updateStatus<br/>→ completed_ocr
    else Confidence < threshold
        rect rgb(254, 243, 199)
            Note over TW: humanGate node<br/>Registers Temporal signal handler<br/>Waits for human approval
            TW -->> HITL: Document enters review queue<br/>(GET /api/hitl/queue)
            Note over HITL: Reviewer creates session<br/>Field-by-field correction<br/>Approve / Escalate / Skip
            HITL -->> TS: Signal: humanApproval<br/>(approved: true)
            TS -->> TW: Signal received
        end
        TW ->> DB: ocr.storeResults<br/>(upsert OcrResult)
        TW ->> DB: document.updateStatus<br/>→ completed_ocr
    end

    Note over TW,ADI: MULTI-PAGE PATH (alternative workflow)

    rect rgb(236, 253, 245)
        Note over TW,ADI: Multi-page documents use map/join nodes
        TW ->> Blob: document.split<br/>(qpdf → segments)
        loop map node (per segment, maxConcurrency)
            TW ->> TS: childWorkflow<br/>(standard OCR per segment)
            TS ->> TW: child result
            TW ->> TW: document.classify<br/>(rule-based segment type)
        end
        TW ->> TW: join node<br/>(collect all segment results)
        TW ->> TW: document.validateFields<br/>(cross-segment validation)
        TW ->> DB: ocr.storeResults
    end

    Note over Source,HITL: DOWNSTREAM CONSUMPTION

    Source ->> BE: GET /api/documents/:id
    BE ->> DB: SELECT Document + OcrResult
    BE -->> Source: Document with extracted data
